I am trying to figure out why a campaign was rejected

Ad rejection reasons are unique to each ad. Some common reasons include incorrect conversion tracking setup for tCPA campaigns or typographical errors. Ad Support will inform you of the specifics via your email. I recommend checking out our advertising policy before submitting ads to avoid future rejections. For more details, you can refer to this article: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next).
i am still looking for the rejection reason

If you haven't received an email with the rejection reason, please check your spam or junk folder. The email should have the subject line ‘Urgent: Ad Rejected - Action Required.’ If you still can't find it, I recommend reaching out to ad support at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
